
0. Follow steps: https://fpgmaas.github.io/cookiecutter-poetry/tutorial/
1. Install homebrew: https://brew.sh/
2. Set up homebrew:
  ```
  echo 'eval $(/opt/homebrew/bin/brew shellenv)' >> ~/.zprofile
  eval $(/opt/homebrew/bin/brew shellenv)
    
  ```
3. install pyenv
  ```
  brew update
  brew install pyenv
  ```
